            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>Tertia. Lived for 40 years.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" resp="#AA">
                <p>The plaque is very simple, recording only one name for the deceased, and her age in years. Another Tertia, a freedwoman, is atteseted in Thermae Himeraeae, <ref target="http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000054">ISic000054</ref>.</p>
